head_commit.message:
Add task to perform server selection driven by GeoIP. (#5398)

* Add task to perform server selection driven by GeoIP.
* Add fallback to random server selection
* Implement functional test mock for ipinfo endpoint
* Add model for the client location
* Move server selection task into ServerCountryModel::pickBest()
* Add unit tests for the Location model
